
1. create Web3Citizen contract
2. mint as many NFTs as we want, but only one NFT per msg.sender
3. Create a Ballot passing in a. list of Proposals b. Address of Web3Citizen contract
4. Register to vote by calling Ballot.registerToVote(); NOTE: NEW STEP
4. Call Ballot.vote() and verify msg.sender owns a Web3Citizen NFT (call Web3Citizen.balanceOf(msg.sender))
5. Ballot calls Web3Citizen.vote() to update the NFT